            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once very hot, add the<strong> spice crusted steaks </strong>to the pan</p><p>For rare, cook for 2 min max on each side; for medium-rare, cook for 2-3 min on each side; for medium, cook for 3-4 min on each side</p><p>Once the steaks are cooked, transfer them to a plate to rest</p>",
