    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a bowl with the <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and juice of the <strong>orange<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Add 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[5 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>chipotle & orange dressing</strong></p><p>Tip: Taste the dressing and add a pinch of sugar if it needs it</p>",
